Package: emergeR
Type: Package
Title: Analysis of EMERGe High-Throughput Editing Data
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
 person("Anthony", "Surkov", email = "anthonysurkov@gmail.com",
 role = c("aut", "cre"))
 )
Description: Tools for processing, modeling, and visualizing EMERGe
 (En Masse Evaluation of RNA Guides) high-throughput editing datasets,
 including beta-binomial statistics, MCA/t-SNE embeddings, HDBSCAN clustering,
 and motif visualization.
